                <li> <img src="/assets/checkmark-circle-outline 1.png" alt="checkmark-circle-outline">Long burning: No more waste. Created for last long.</li>
            </ul>
            <button class="features_button">Learn more</button>
        </section>
        <section class="features_right">
            <img src="/assets/image.png" alt="image">
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
